                <h1>The iPhone as a roadblock</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/e4353efb-cfd2-4b90-9f8f-b33f0581847b.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="Photo&#x20;courtesy&#x20;of&#x20;Wikipedia" class="w-100">
